{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2130183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "换句话说，房东正是新地主阶级", "timestamp": 1627184179, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "落了片白茫茫大地真干净!", "timestamp": 1627184220, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "白毛女听了想杀人", "timestamp": 1627184348, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130197, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "古代的粮食收成不能和现在比吧", "timestamp": 1627184351, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有点好奇dz的经济状况", "timestamp": 1627184473, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130204, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "您稍微读读茅盾的《春蚕》《林家铺子》，柳青的《创业谱》，周立波的《暴风骤雨》，丁玲的《太阳照在桑干河上》，也不会有地主社会好的想法", "timestamp": 1627184482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": 2130204, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: dz是在讽刺现在的社会。。", "timestamp": 1627184553, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130209, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《创业史》，打错了", "timestamp": 1627184556, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130213, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不是想说地主好，dz当然对地主这种不劳而获的食利阶层是很痛恨的", "timestamp": 1627184652, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130216, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同样被抽走30%，古代的农民经常揭不开锅，而现在的打工人情况好一点，是因为总收入相对于以前多一些么？", "timestamp": 1627184721, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 240, "w": 320}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1627184730, "type": "image", "url": "bp/bp73ldacefccjriwr55j5lssdui4ea3h.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2130231, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实这个也得看地区和时代（", "timestamp": 1627184934, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "地主是一个完全的食利的统治阶级，占用生产资料，享受大部分劳动果实。古代统治者所谓统治智慧大部分就是休养生息，劝课农桑，无为而治。仅从这一点看来，房东和地主很像。但是，在现代社会，国家依靠税收进行收入再分配，房东自己也要接受收入再分配", "timestamp": 1627185051, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "地主抽佃农30%是因为再抽取更多，佃农就要饿死了，佃农从唐宋之后才渐渐得到自由流动的可能；房东收你30%是因为再抽取更多，你就去别家租房了；对比封建生产，资本主义还是先进一些", "timestamp": 1627185778, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130323, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在生物科技没有发展的以前，每亩地收的粮食远不如现在，而且，农民还得担忧天灾。一般情况下30%可以保证佃农饿不死，但是遇上天灾，粮食不够吃，只能找地主借高利贷的粮食，于是利滚利利滚利，最后被逼无奈，甚至只能卖儿卖女。", "timestamp": 1627186336, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130342, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在dz这孩子站到为资产阶级辩护的立场前，应该还有的救", "timestamp": 1627186684, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130393, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz再看看自己劳动创造的价值有百分之多少是发给你的工资……多少变成了高管的工资，多少变成了股份分红给了公司股票的所有者？再想想dz未来的孩子是不是可能也要给房东的孩子打工？把思路打开，当前的这一点点问题就只是小问题了", "timestamp": 1627187117, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2134041, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 413190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "30是发善心的时候吧，大部分时候没这么低", "timestamp": 1627228077, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 413190, "reply": 18, "tag": null, "text": "dz刚了解到古代的地主对佃农的抽成大概是30%，联想到dz正好大概30%的工资要交给房东，这么看来封建社会的剥削也不是很严重啊", "timestamp": 1627184120, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627228075, "url": "", "vote": {}}}